window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>From<i> New York Times </i>and<i> USA Today </i>best-selling author Angela Snyder comes a new stand-alone, full-length romantic suspense novel.</p> <p>I was forced to marry a monster.</p> <p>Luca Vitale is the heir to his father’s empire.</p> <p>He has the reputation of being a dangerous monster who can bring even grown men to their knees.</p> <p>And he’s about to become my husband.</p> <p>Our families have been at war with one another ever since I can remember. </p> <p>I am the daughter of his enemy, and he will try everything to control me, to bend me...to break me. </p> <p>When I’m forced to make a deal with the devil himself, one question still remains—will our union be one of love or violence?</p> <p>Note:<i> Keeping My Bride</i> is the first book in the Keeping What's Mine series, but each book in the series can be listened to as a stand-alone. It is a dark mafia arranged-marriage romance. It contains adult content for mature listeners.</p>"; 
